          </div>
          <div class="info mb-5">
            <h6>(A) Security Rules</h6>
            <ul>
              <li>
                <p><span class="icon"><i class="icofont-check-circled"></i></span> Refundable Deposit is applicable only
                  for (20L Water). Customers will be able to identify such brands clearly whilst placing their orders.
                </p>
              </li>
              <li>
                <p><span class="icon"><i class="icofont-check-circled"></i></span> Customers can initiate Refund from
                  their Order History.</p>
              </li>
              <li>
                <p><span class="icon"><i class="icofont-check-circled"></i></span> Whenever a customer wants rebate on
                  the deposit, customer has to initiate a refund request with Click Your Order.com. It is reviewed and
                  paid only if the following conditions are met.</p>
              </li>
              <li>
                <p><span class="icon"><i class="icofont-check-circled"></i></span> Customer has to return the empty jars
                  in the same condition as received from CLICK YOUR ORDER and / or it’s Sellers.</p>
              </li>
              <li>
                <p><span class="icon"><i class="icofont-check-circled"></i></span> Customer has to request a refund
                  within 60 days from the last order placed in Click Your Order.com. Customers forfeit their rebate if
                  they did not place any order for 60 days from their last order.</p>
              </li>
              <li>
                <p><span class="icon"><i class="icofont-check-circled"></i></span> CLICK YOUR ORDER deducts 20% from the
                  original deposit amount towards processing, depreciation charges and pay the balance to customer.</p>
              </li>
              <li>
                <p><span class="icon"><i class="icofont-check-circled"></i></span> The processing of refund (after
                  deducting the processing charge incurred) will take maximum 15 working days from the day of refund
                  initiation.</p>
              </li>
              <li>
                <p><span class="icon"><i class="icofont-check-circled"></i></span> Unless a proof of deposit (either
                  invoice/receipt, SMS or email from CLICK YOUR ORDER) is provided, customer will not get refund. Under
                  no circumstances, refund is given without returning the empty jars to CLICK YOUR ORDER or Vendor /
                  Seller.</p>
              </li>
              <li>
                <p><span class="icon"><i class="icofont-check-circled"></i></span> Refund is given only to customers who
                  have deposited with CLICK YOUR ORDER. Under no circumstances, refund is given to customers who did not
                  deposit with CLICK YOUR ORDER</p>
              </li>
              <li>
                <p><span class="icon"><i class="icofont-check-circled"></i></span> Regarding refund requested during
                  delivery due to partial or full cancellation by customer: In case, during delivery at door step,
                  customer wants to cancel the delivery due to non availability of empty jars or whatever reasons, CLICK
                  YOUR ORDER can cancel the order and refund the order amount after deducting service charge. The
                  remaining amount will be credited to customer wallet and the same can be utilized for subsequent
                  orders. The customer is liable to pay service charge despite cancellation of order because delivery
                  team has already incurred cost of logistics.
                </p>
              </li>
            </ul>


            <h6>(B) Cancellation</h6>
            <p>Cancellation charge is applicable as follows:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>
                <p><span class="icon"><i class="icofont-check-circled"></i></span> If Customer cancels the order where
                  the delivery has not started yet, then 5% deduction is applicable from your total Order value.</p>
              </li>
              <li>
                <p><span class="icon"><i class="icofont-check-circled"></i></span> Customer can request to cancel the
                  order (calling our customer care support) where the delivery has already started and in-transit, then
                  the full delivery charge per quantity will be deducted from your total Order value.</p>
              </li>
            </ul>

            <h6>(C) Return</h6>
            <p>All our customers can return the product at the time of delivery only if items arrive in bad condition,
              damaged or leaked. Returns will only be offered if the product is in its original packaging, unopened,
              unused and returned with the same delivery driver on the same delivery day. We will take the returned
              product back with us and a credit note for the value of the return products which will be credited to your
              wallet account, which is not applicable for Payments made upon delivery. This can be used to pay your
              subsequent shopping bills on the site. No return / refund is acceptable for any product that arrives in
              good condition, and CLICK YOUR ORDER has the right to limit or refuse the acceptance of return of certain
              products at any time and for any reason.</p>

            <h6>(D) Can Usage Policy</h6>
            <p>The prevailing market price of an empty Can is approximately Rs.150. CLICK YOUR ORDER has come up with a
              concept of Can Usage option for their customers under which customers pay lesser than the market price for
              their Usage only. At the same time, the empty Can is a property of the Seller(s) who supplied at customers
              door-step hence customers are liable/accountable/responsible for the empty Cans received through this
              option/policy.</p>

            <p>
              If customers have not placed orders (10 orders within 4 months), then the Seller(s) have all rights to
              come and collect the empty Cans from the customers. The customers are liable to return the empty Cans to
              the Seller(s) else balance amount of Rs.75 per Can to be paid to the Seller(s) directly.
            </p>

            <p>
              The Can Usage amount is non-refundable and the customer is not eligible to claim this amount whenever they
              decided to close their account with CLICK YOUR ORDER.
            </p>

